  <description>
	<p>You are the leader of your Roman Empire, but it has only one province. Expand your empire to get more might. Get farmers, denar and soldiers to expand your empire. You need to invade 43 other provinces to finish the game. You gain rewards by learning Latin vocabs. If you want to reset your savegame, simply click RESET in Settings.</p>
